  "texts": [
    "Given the centrality of STEM education in China's reform agenda, addressing this gap is crucial for enhancing teacher effectiveness and improving student outcomes in STEM disciplines.",
    "This study seeks to bridge that gap by systematically reviewing literature from 2016 to 2023 to provide a thorough understanding of STEM TPD programs.",
    "Literature Review STEM TPDs.",
    "In China, STEM education is experiencing robust growth and innovation (Zhou and Li, 2021a, 2021b).",
    "Recognized globally as a vital approach to crafting educational strategies, STEM nurtures critical skills, eloquence, and technological prowess in students (Zou, 2021)."
  ]
}